/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the cityscape. The street, teeming with life, stretches out below, flanked by buildings on both sides. These structures, predominantly gray and white, rise up to meet the clear blue sky. A few trees interspersed among the buildings add a touch of green to the urban landscape. The sun shines brightly, casting a warm glow over the scene. The image is slightly distorted due to the fisheye lens effect, adding a unique perspective to the photograph.
